06:47.900 --> 06:49.622
Well, what are we going to do?

06:49.642 --> 06:51.985
The thing is designed.

06:52.005 --> 06:54.348
We've got, you know, their grand design.

06:55.009 --> 06:58.133
And what are we going to do about the shelving?

06:58.473 --> 07:00.716
Well, it's a public project.

07:00.897 --> 07:08.787
