07:09.187 --> 07:14.454
No, the Department of Public Works was overseeing this project.

07:14.714 --> 07:17.738
And the library was not even the client.

07:18.646 --> 07:23.814
The library was the sort of peripheral, but they were supposed to be overseeing it for expenditure.

07:23.834 --> 07:36.454
I mean, mainly, it would be kept on the hundred million dollars, and the architects were constantly fighting that or ignoring what we were saying about what our needs were in terms of money, because they were trying to make this grand thing.

07:38.156 --> 07:39.859
We lost that space for books.

07:39.879 --> 07:41.081
I said, what are we going to do?

07:41.341 --> 07:42.704
Are we going to call the halls?

07:42.864 --> 07:44.627
I was her assistant.

07:44.647 --> 07:46.830
Ah, you were Captain Cage's assistant?

