14:53.219 --> 14:53.520
You don't know.

14:53.540 --> 14:53.700
Exactly.

14:53.798 --> 14:57.503
And probably the library doesn't know either.

14:57.543 --> 15:05.915
Well, it was even more controversial because the New Mains put all the periodicals in one place and took them from the subject department.

15:05.936 --> 15:14.748
