This is part of the legacy, Kathy Page's legacy, is that she...

15:22.486 --> 15:24.529
insisted on this.

15:24.729 --> 15:33.340
This is what happened with the New Main Library being so small, and she made sure that those periodicals were put into Brooks Hall.

15:33.920 --> 15:35.563
The librarians had to do it.

15:36.424 --> 15:47.818
They had to follow her instructions, and then she also was the one who started panicking and called for the weeding of the books in Brooks Hall, which

15:48.693 --> 15:51.957
which moved to the weeding of books.

