24:14.226 --> 24:16.528
And that pitch about it is basically what she said.

24:16.888 --> 24:21.272
So I guess the reason I mention this is... What can we do?

24:21.473 --> 24:24.075
That's why I say, look, you've got a $200 million thing over there.

