26:05.246 --> 26:06.688
It's all mixed in with office space.

26:06.708 --> 26:09.291
So huge areas, and...

26:09.625 --> 26:18.167
There's not much you can do about that, but maybe there's, I don't know, but maybe there's some way to put parts of the collection of books that could be browsed.

26:18.535 --> 26:22.099
But you need the librarians near the... You need to cover up the light walls.

26:22.119 --> 26:23.361
I mean, there are things that they can do.

26:23.441 --> 26:25.283
They can make more floor spaces.

26:25.303 --> 26:26.965
I don't know what they can do.

