27:51.083 --> 27:52.425
We didn't need to sell it.

27:52.445 --> 27:54.928
That building in order to remain.

27:55.128 --> 27:58.812
And since we didn't sell it, maybe we should get some other piece of property for free.

27:58.932 --> 28:00.714
And the money to fix it up.

28:00.835 --> 28:01.175
I know.

